  \   Save current item and append a new item below it\nCTRL+Enter     Save current
  item and append a new item above it\nCTRL+Left      Indent the item one time to
  the left. \nCTRL+Right     Indent the item one time to the right.\nCTRL+Up        Save
  current item and edit item above it\nCTRL+Down      Save current item and edit item
  below it \nCTRL+B         Bold\nCTRL+I         Italic\nCTRL+U         Underline\nCTRL+H
  \        Highlight\nCTRL+N         Add a line break\n\na    Add a new item to the
  bottom \nA    Add a new item to the top \n/    Moves the focus to the query box\ns
  \   Sort items by date \np    Sort items by priority \nr    Toggle item reorder
  mode \nR    Toggle project reorder mode\n?    Shows this window (i.e. shows shortcuts)\n\nSingle
  click on item     Edit the item\nShift-Click on checkbox  Force move to history
  of item and its children\nShift-Click on priority  Set the priority of item and
  not its children"
